criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients of both sexes;

          -  aged 18 years or older;

          -  diagnosed with ACS (unstable angina and acute myocardial infarction with ST segment
             elevation and without ST segment elevation) with CAD diagnosed by cardiac
             catheterization or electrocardiogram;

          -  patients have to agree to participate by signing a consent term

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with cognitive deficits;

          -  neurological sequelae;

          -  who are not able to come for visits, or who do not consent to participate in the
             study.
